
%input file for DOTB
%Discrete Ordinates with Two BrainCells


% name of the problem:

Name BWR-Cell

% tolerances:
tol 1E-7 1E-5
maxit 100

% (cell length, number of mesh) is given as tupple in sequence
% cellx left to right
% celly bottom to top

CellX (1.5, 1) (6.4, 1) (1.0, 1)
CellY (1.5, 1) (6.4, 1) (1.0, 1) 
refinement 4

% boundary condition:
%   B   T   L   R

BC  1   1   1   1

% Quadrature set:
SN 4

% material and cross section file:

xsfile BWR_cell.xs

% material correspondig to each pair CellX CellY
% insert left to right, top to bottom, parser does the flipping
MatMap
2 2 2
2 1 2
2 2 2
